Applying for Financial Aid

  • Candidates who wish to apply for Financial Aid need to create a SUNet ID, upload required documents, and contact the Financial Aid Office by April 1 to ensure that a financial aid offer is available in advance of the April 30, Plan to Enroll deadline.
  • To create the Stanford SUNet ID, your University ID is required: [[UNIVERSITYID]]
  • For additional information on Financial Aid, please see the Financial Aid tab on the navigation menu on the left.
Accepted Candidates must either select Plan to Enroll or Withdraw on or before April 30
To Plan to Enroll
  • If not yet done, create your Stanford SUNet ID. Your University ID is required: [[UNIVERSITYID]]
  • Register your decision to "Plan to Enroll" in Stanford MedAdmit
  • Register your decision to "Plan to Enroll" using Choose Your Medical School Tool
To Withdraw
  • Use Stanford MedAdmit to withdraw your application
Contact
  • If you have any questions or concerns, please email mdaccepted@stanford.edu
